            <h2>Create a New Account</h2>

<p></p>
<p>
  APS Journal accounts provide a single username and password for all APS online services for readers, authors, referees, and members.
  <b>Please note that an APS Journal account is distinct from old referee logins based on six digit referee IDs as well as from previously set up accounts for submitting papers to APS journals.</b>
</p>
<p>APS members who already have an APS Member Web account for accessing membership services may choose to use the same username and password. To do so, please log in below using the form labeled "Use APS Member Web Account" and your APS Member account information. All others should use the form labeled "Create a new username"</p>
<p>Please read the <a href="http://www.aps.org/about/privacy.cfm">APS Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="http://publish.aps.org/policies/terms.html">Terms and Conditions</a> before creating your account. By creating an account, you are agreeing to these policies.</p>
<div id='signup'>
  <div id='memberbox'>
    <h3>Use APS Member Web Account</h3>
    <form class="form-horizontal" method="post" action="/signup/member" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='uname'>Username:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="uname" name="user[username]" type="text" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='pw'>Password:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="pw" name="user[password]" type="password" /></div>
    </div>
    <input class='btn btn-primary' type='submit' value='Log in' />
    </form>
    <div id='login-helper-links'>
      <a href="https://www.aps.org/memb-sec/membership/pwdreset.cfm">Forgot your username/password?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id='signupbox'>
    <h3>Create a new username</h3>
    <form method="post" class="form-horizontal" action="/account" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='uname'>Username:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="uname" tabindex="1" class="" name="user[username]" type="text" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='password'>Password:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="password" tabindex="2" class="" name="user[password]" type="password" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='password_confirmation'>Password (again):</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="password_confirmation" tabindex="3" class="" name="user[password_confirmation]" type="password" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='realname'>Real Name:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="realname" tabindex="4" class="" name="user[real_name]" type="text" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <label class='control-label' for='email'>Email Address:</label>
      <div class='controls'><input id="email" tabindex="5" class="" name="user[primary_email]" type="text" /></div>
    </div>
    <input class='btn btn-primary' tabindex='6' type='submit' value='Create' />
    </form>
  </div>
